          <p class="font-italic"><small>Graphic Designer</small></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="testimonial text-left">
      <p class="font-italic mb-2">“I was having a hard time focusing in co-working spaces and couldn't get any work done. Homey changed everything!”</p>
      <div class="d-flex">
